1:26 dia\ tou=to pare/dwken au)tou\s o( qeo\j ei)j pa/qh a)timi/aj: ai(/ te ga\r qh/leiai au)tw=n meth/llacan th\n fusikh\n xrh=sin ei)j th\n para\ fu/sin,
