3:5 ei) de\ h( a)diki/a h(mw=n qeou= dikaiosu/nhn suni/sthsin, ti/ e)rou=men; mh\ a)/dikoj o( qeo\j o( e)pife/rwn th\n o)rgh/n; kata\ a)/nqrwpon le/gw.
