4:6 kaqa/per kai\ Dauei\d le/gei to\n makarismo\n tou= a)nqrw/pou w(=| o( qeo\j logi/zetai dikaiosu/nhn xwri\j e)/rgwn,
4:7 maka/rioi w(=n a)fe/qhsan ai( a)nomi/ai kai\ w(=n e)pekalu/fqhsan ai( a(marti/ai:
