12:1 Parakalw= ou)=n u(ma=j, a)delfoi/, dia\ tw=n oi)ktirmw=n tou= qeou=, parasth=sai ta\ sw/mata u(mw=n qusi/an zw=san a(gi/an tw=| qew=| eu)a/reston, th\n logikh\n latrei/an u(mw=n:
